<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nova Search - Results</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <style>
        /* Professional results page styling */
        body {
            background: #0a0e27 !important;
            background-image: none !important;
        }

        .results-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 80px 20px 40px 20px;
            text-align: left;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .back-navigation {
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .back-btn {
            color: #38bdf8;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12);
            transform: translateX(-4px);
            color: #0ea5e9;
            border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
        }

        .results-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
        }

        .results-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            cursor: pointer;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8 0%, #a78bfa 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            letter-spacing: -1.2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 0;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .results-header h2:hover {
            transform: scale(1.08);
        }

        .search-term-display {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15) 0%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.15) 100%);
            border: 2px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.35);
            padding: 16px 28px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #e0e7ff;
            font-weight: 700;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 500px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .search-term-display:hover {
            border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.5);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
        }

        .search-term-display strong {
            color: #38bdf8;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 0.7px;
            text-transform: capitalize;
        }

        .results-info {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
        }

        .results-info strong {
            color: #e0e7ff;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .simulated-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 100%);
            border: 2px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            transition: all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .simulated-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s ease;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .simulated-card:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .simulated-card:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10) 100%);
            border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.6);
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25), 0 0 60px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
        }

        .simulated-card a {
            color: #38bdf8;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 900;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            letter-spacing: -0.7px;
            text-transform: capitalize;
        }

        .simulated-card a:hover {
            color: #0ea5e9;
            transform: translateX(6px);
        }

        .simulated-card p {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            margin-top: 14px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .simulated-card strong {
            color: #e0e7ff;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        .results-empty {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        .results-empty p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        .results-empty p:first-child {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #e0e7ff;
        }

        .results-footer {
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding-top: 40px;
            border-top: 2px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .results-footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .results-footer strong {
            color: #38bdf8;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        /* Responsive design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .results-container {
                padding: 60px 16px 30px 16px;
            }

            .results-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 16px;
            }

            .search-term-display {
                max-width: 100%;
                width: 100%;
            }

            .results-header h2 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }

            .simulated-card {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .simulated-card a {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .simulated-card p {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .results-container {
                padding: 50px 12px 20px 12px;
            }

            .results-header h2 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }

            .search-term-display {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                padding: 10px 16px;
            }

            .simulated-card {
                padding: 16px;
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }

            .simulated-card a {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .simulated-card p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="justify-content: flex-start; align-items: stretch;">

    <div class="results-container">
        <div class="back-navigation">
            <a href="index.html" class="back-btn"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left-long"></i> Return to Search</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="results-header">
            <h2 onclick="window.location.href='index.html'" title="Back to NovaSearch">
                <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8 0%, #38bdf8 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">Nova</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="search-term-display">
                <i class="fas fa-search" style="color: #38bdf8; margin-right: 8px;"></i>
                <strong id="query-target">...</strong>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="results-info">
            Search Results for <strong id="query-display">...</strong>
        </div>

        <div id="results-list">
        </div>

        <div class="results-footer">
            <p>Powered by <strong>NovaSearch</strong> • Enterprise-Grade AI Search Engine</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
            // Grab the search query from URL parameters
            const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
            const query = urlParams.get('q') || '';
            const type = urlParams.get('type') || 'all';

            // Display the query in both places
            document.getElementById("query-target").textContent = query;
            document.getElementById("query-display").textContent = query;

            // Generate mock search results dynamically
            const resultsList = document.getElementById("results-list");
            
            if(query.trim() === "") {
                resultsList.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="results-empty">
                        <p>No Search Query Provided</p>
                        <p style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #64748b;">Please return to NovaSearch and enter a search query to display results.</p>
                    </div>
                `;
                return;
            }

            resultsList.innerHTML = `
                <div class="simulated-card">
                    <a href="#">Executive Summary: ${query}</a>
                    <p>Comprehensive analysis and strategic intelligence on <strong>${query}</strong>. NovaSearch's advanced AI algorithms have curated premium results from authoritative sources, delivering enterprise-grade insights optimized for <strong>${type}</strong> research with 99.9% accuracy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="simulated-card">
                    <a href="#">Technical Resources & Documentation</a>
                    <p>Access professional documentation, technical specifications, and architectural frameworks related to <strong>${query}</strong>. Our platform aggregates verified information from industry leaders and peer-reviewed sources to provide authoritative guidance for informed decision-making.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="simulated-card">
                    <a href="#">Market Trends & Industry Analysis</a>
                    <p>Stay competitive with current market trends and expert analysis on <strong>${query}</strong>. NovaSearch leverages machine learning and real-time data integration to identify emerging patterns and deliver actionable intelligence for strategic planning and research.</p>
                </div>
            `;
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
                return;
            }

            resultsList.innerHTML = `
                <div class="simulated-card">
                    <a href="#">Top Custom Result for "${query}"</a>
                    <p>This is a simulated search matching your request. Nova engine processed your data structure natively under the <strong>${type}</strong> category matrix.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="simulated-card">
                    <a href="#">Exploring Information Architectures</a>
                    <p>Discover academic files, technical project frameworks, and documentation regarding "${query}" compiled dynamically on the frontend interface.</p>
                </div>
            `;
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>